snippet.title: Nameless Cat - Android Release Trailer
snippet.description:
🏆 Honorable Mention Award in 2018 Bahamut ACG Creation Contest 🏆

Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.kotobagames.namelesscat
iOS: https://apps.apple.com/us/app/id1478510294

"Oh, you know, many have given up halfway" —— God

The long-awaited action game -- Nameless Cat is finally coming to Google Play Store!
Nameless Cat is a pixel art game, enriched with puzzle-solving elements and OST.
Immersed in stunning visuals and beautiful soundtracks, you are transformed into an adorable kitten and entering a feast for your senses!

| Official Sites |
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/KotobaGames/
